MATRIX NUMERICAL COMPUTING SYSTEM (C++)

==================================================

1. OVERVIEW
   ==================================================

This project is a modular numerical computing system built in C++ using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) principles.

It supports:

* Matrix operations (Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division)
* Solving linear equations using:

  * Gauss Elimination (Direct Method)
  * Gauss Jacobi (Iterative Method)
  * Gauss Seidel (Iterative Method)
  * LU Decomposition

The system is designed as a CLI (Command Line Interface) tool with:

* User input (terminal or file)
* Output (terminal or file)
* Expandable architecture

---

==================================================
